U.S. May Drop Charges Against Credit Suisse Banker, NZZ Says

-- B y   D e r m o t   D o h e r t y
-- 
2011-04-24T11:00:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-24/u-s-may-drop-charges-against-credit-suisse-banker-nzz-says.html
U.S. authorities may drop charges
against  Credit Suisse Group AG (CSGN)  banker Christos Bagios by May 12
over his alleged involvement in tax evasion, NZZ am Sonntag
reported, citing a document from the Fort Lauderdale district
court.  Credit Suisse declined to comment, according to the e-
mailed pre-release of an article in the  newspaper .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dermot Doherty in Geneva at 
 ddoherty9@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
